\id 2JN - Numanggang NT (with Gen, Ex, Ps) [nop] -Papua New Guinea 2005 (DBL 2017)
\h 2 Jon
\toc1 Jondi pepa lekiŋgoŋ youkuk
\toc2 2 Jon
\toc3 2Jn
\mt1 Jondi pepa lekiŋgoŋ youkuk
\imt1 Yodakale Mede
\ip Pepa yoŋ adi kayoŋbop niŋ’walaŋ talitimeŋ niŋdi youkuk. Meeniŋ feedi indiŋ nadiiŋ, pepa yoŋ adi kayoŋbop niŋdok youyemguk. Tiŋa nehi uŋgoŋ hekinolit biyagoŋ hinek tiŋa hatiŋila yalaŋ-me heki Bepaŋ’walaŋ mede yotubugiyonda tiiŋ heki fiyeŋ doktiŋa kikaulidoko tiyaneeŋdok yeniŋguk.
\c 1
\s1 Yodakale eŋ welemomooŋ mede
\p 
\v 1 Nu kayoŋbop diniŋ me talitimeŋ timeniŋdi tam\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Nadinadi me nolidi tam wondok adi indiŋ nadiiŋ, kayoŋbop adi’walaŋ yolineŋ bopneyagiŋ. Kaŋ nadinadime nolidi indiŋ nadiiŋ. Jon adi kayoŋbopdok nadiŋa “tam” youkuk.\f* Bepaŋdi netok gigit gabukahileguk tiŋa wapmihigeye hiditok pepa i youhamulat. Nu mede biyagoŋ welene gineŋ hatak wondoktiŋa welenedi habukahile hinek tilat. Tiŋa nu kubugoŋdi hogok mu tilat, mokoŋ. Adi metam mede biyagoŋ nadiŋa nadidahi tiiŋ heki adi maaŋ welehikdi habukahile hinek tiiŋ.
\v 2 Mede biyagoŋdi indi’walaŋ welenik gineŋ hatak, wondi haliwooŋ halaak, wendoktiŋa hekinolit folooŋ hinek hatiyam.
\v 3 Indi mede biyagoŋnit eŋ me hekinolit hatihati folooŋ hinek hatinene Baŋ Bepaŋ tiŋa Jesu Kilisto Me Baŋ’walaŋ Mihiŋiŋ adi’walaŋ siloŋ tobogoŋ, welekulema eŋ kulemaŋiŋ wendi indi’walaŋkade haliwooŋ halaak.
\s1 Me Hekinolit momooŋ tiŋa hatidok mede
\p 
\v 4 Wapmihigeye noli adi Me Baŋdi yodoko medeŋiŋ niniŋguk u tagimneeŋ mede biyagoŋ u kedem beŋa hatiiŋ, mebihik unduŋ nadiŋa nadifo hinek tilat.
\v 5 Ale tam loloŋnit, du yodoko mede niŋ ganimbe nadiweŋ. Mede u kobuli moŋ. Koomkwaha tububihit gineŋ tububihila naditalabam uŋakoŋ indiŋ ganimbit. Metam nadisukilitihinit indi hekinolit momooŋ tiŋa hatiyaneem.
\v 6 Bepaŋ’walaŋ yodoko mede tagimneeŋ kelekele wondi me hekinolit hatihati uŋakoŋ tilak. Ale Bepaŋ’walaŋ yodoko mede koom tububihila nadigiŋdi naditalabiiŋ u indiŋ uŋakoŋ. Hidi hatihatihik gineŋ me hekinolit momooŋ tiŋa hatiyaneeŋ.
\s1 Mede yotubugiyonda me hekidok mede
\p 
\v 7 I nadineŋ, tikamanda me feedi mintaaŋ kwetkwet hatidapmaiŋ. Adi Jesu Kilisto kwetfoloŋ sigiŋ gitnemnit mintaguk u nadiune folooŋ mu tilak. Me undiniŋ uŋakoŋ yalaŋ-me eŋ Kilisto’walaŋ memikŋiŋ unduŋ niniŋdok.
\p 
\v 8 Hidi’walaŋkade kwanai tinene folooŋ mintaguk u tiyaugene fihambaakneŋ doktiŋa momooŋgoŋ hinek kadokooŋ hatiyaneeŋ. Ala hatigene kougoŋ tuwaŋiŋ wendok tuwolit hinek beneeŋ.
\v 9 Nebek niŋ Kilisto’walaŋ medeŋiŋ mu tihifafaŋeeŋ mede noli foloŋ wooŋ galiwaak, adi yadi Bepaŋ tuwot mu kahilewaak. Eŋ me nediyeŋ Kilisto’walaŋ medeŋiŋ tihifafaŋewaak adi yadi Baŋ gut Mihi wanakaŋ yabukahilewaak.
\v 10 Eŋ me niŋdi mede gitipmuŋgoŋ niŋ tiŋa hidi’walaŋkade buune kaŋ niutumba tiŋa nagila yohineŋ adi mu kameyaneeŋ.
\v 11 Nebek niŋdi me undiniŋ niutumba tibaak, adi yadi me wendi’walaŋ kwanaiŋiŋ hogoli u tubulodawaak.
\s1 Yodapmaŋ mede
\p 
\v 12 Mede mohok noli maaŋ hakiiŋ, iŋgoŋ pepa foloŋ youhamdok mu nadilat. Nu adi tobo buŋa habuŋa manikdi kiyonadi titiŋdok nadilat. Unduŋ tiŋa nadifo kedem tineem.
\v 13 Dalage Bepaŋdi agaŋ kahileguk adi’walaŋ wapmihiŋiyedi youtumba mede kamegamiiŋ. 
